name: Alby #Colony: Three 1,3
description: The 3rd piece in the Alby #Colony collection.  The Alby Wistar #Colony collection will be a limited series of 42 pieces, all 1/1.  Each depicting differently inspired backgrounds, relating to the Alby Wistar concept (see Genesis) and "Uniquely Generic" theme (see also, Alby #Mischief collection).
